or to any other address notified by either party in accordance with this Article. Notices shall be deemed to have been validly given when made by: (i) personal delivery against receipt, (ii) registered letter with return receipt requested, (iii) letter delivered by international postal services or any equivalent service, or (iv) fax or email
 
