which these options were granted, has provided the flexibility to permit me to make the election voluntarily as I deem appropriate. I acknowledge that I understand that the Company's stock plans provide that, after I properly complete and deliver this election, all of my discount options covered by a valid election will be amended automatically as described in this election form.
I acknowledge that once I make an election under this procedure, it is deemed to be irrevocable as of April 25, 2008 and thus I may not later change my decision with respect to any portion of this election. However, the Company does reserve the right to cancel or replace, or allow employees to cancel or replace, this election to the extent permitted or required by subsequent changes in the tax law.
