Item 2.02. Results of Operations and Financial Condition
On July 30, 2008, Atmel Corporation ("Atmel" or the "Company") issued a press release discussing its financial results for the second quarter ended June 30, 2008. The press release is attached hereto as Exhibit 99.1 and is incorporated herein by reference.
