     Your signature below indicates your agreement and understanding that this Award is subject to and governed by the terms and conditions of the Plan and this Award Agreement. For example, important additional information on vesting and forfeiture of the Restricted Stock Units is contained in paragraphs 3 through 5 of Exhibit A. PLEASE BE SURE TO READ ALL OF EXHIBIT A AND EXHIBIT B, WHICH CONTAIN THE SPECIFIC TERMS AND CONDITIONS OF THIS AWARD AGREEMENT. You further represent that you have reviewed the Plan and this Award Agreement in their entirety, have had an opportunity to obtain the advice of counsel prior to executing this Award Agreement and fully understand all provisions of the Plan and Award Agreement. You hereby agree to accept as binding, conclusive and final all decisions or interpretations of the Administrator upon any questions relating to the Plan and Award Agreement. You further agree to notify the Company upon any change in the residence address indicated below.
 
