Item 2.05. Costs Associated with Exit or Disposal Activities
On December 12, 2008, the board of directors of Atmel Corporation (the "Company") approved, and on December 15, 2008 the Company announced, a workforce reduction of approximately 285 employees, or 11%, of the Company's North American workforce, to be complete by the end of the Company's 2009 first fiscal quarter. The Company estimates that it will incur restructuring charges of approximately $4 million related to cash severance payments.
A copy of the press release relating to this announcement is attached hereto as Exhibit 99.1 and is incorporated herein by reference.
Item 9.01. Financial Statements and Exhibits
