5.3. Atmel acknowledges that these monetary settlement payments and corporate governance reforms confer substantial benefits upon Atmel and Current Atmel Shareholders.
     5.3 The Settling Parties have conducted extensive negotiations over an extended period of time and have reached agreement that, within thirty days of the Effective Date, Atmel shall, if it has not done so already, adopt the corporate governance reforms set forth below.
