     7.2 Within ten days after execution of this Agreement, State Plaintiffs' Counsel shall notify each of the State Courts of this Agreement and shall apply to each of the State Courts for a stay of all proceedings pending entry of the Final Federal Judgment.
     7.3 Within ten days after entry of the Final Federal Judgment, State Plaintiffs' Counsel shall seek dismissal with prejudice of their respective State Actions and shall use their best efforts to secure the Final State Judgments.
