     That the proper officers of the Company are authorized and directed, for and on behalf of the Company and in its name, to execute and file with the Secretary of State of the State of Delaware a certificate of elimination relating to the Series A Preferred Stock, and to take such further actions as he may deem necessary or appropriate to carry out the intent of the foregoing resolutions in accordance with the applicable provisions of the DGCL."
RESOLVED FURTHER:
     3. Accordingly, all matters set forth in the Certificate of Designation with respect to the Series A Preferred Stock be, and hereby are, eliminated from the Restated Certificate of Incorporation, as heretofore amended, of the Company.
