Approval of the 2010 Employee Stock Purchase Plan and Reservation of Shares
At the Annual Meeting of Stockholders of Atmel Corporation ("" or the "") held on May 19, 2010 (the ""), the stockholders of Atmel voted on and approved the Atmel 2010 Employee Stock Purchase Plan (the "") and the reservation of 25,000,000 shares of common stock for issuance thereunder.
